title: <NextUtah/> Kickoff Event
description: all about the <NextUtah/> Kickoff Event on March 21st, 2024

body.raw:
When: March 21st, 2024 @ 6:00 PM MST

Where: 519 W State St #201, Pleasant Grove, UT 84062

## Presentations

App directory & server actions by Mitchell Wright

RAG w/ Vercel AI SDK & NextJS by Cameron Youngblood

shadcn/ui & component design by Bridger Tower

More coming soon...

## Speakers

[Mitchell Wright](https://twitter.com/mitchellbwright), Analytics Engineer @ Vercel

[Cameron Youngblood](https://twitter.com/youngbloodcyb), Full Stack Engineer @ Ampry

[Bridger Tower](https://twitter.com/bridgertower), Design Engineer @ Ampry

More coming soon...

<Button asChild href="https://tally.so/r/w51OKQ">
  RSVP for free!
</Button>
